hanics. In this paper I lift this restriction. In\neach case I reduce the relational problem to a standard one, thus obtain\nvarious exact, asymptotic and numerical solutions, and then recast these into\nthe original mechanical variables for physical interpretation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 6 Sep 2008 14:19:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Sep 2008 00:03:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 13 Apr 2009 17:58:13 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 23 Sep 2009 23:57:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-24"}
